#-d /**
#-d   \brief hardware script for EL5042
#-d   \details 2 channel BISS-C encoder interface
#-d   \author Anders Sandstroem
#-d   \file
#-d   \note SDOS
#-d   \param [out] SDO 0x1011:01 --> 1684107116 \b reset
